com.mystique.rt.getmydrivercardapplcation.apputils

Class RememberAll

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mystique.rt.getmydrivercardapplcation.apputils.RememberAll

  • public class RememberAll
extends java.lang.Object

    RememberAll class

    Description: This class handles the functionality for initializing and updating the key Objects in this application (Picture, Driver, CardApplicationForm). It is publicly available through a static instance accessed by all fragments in the "slider" view. It facilitates the assembling of objects over a number of different fragments and various steps in preparation for their saving to the database. It also serves as a means of "saving the state" of fragment views as the user slides through them.
    Since:
    2018-11-12
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Mystique Team
